Package: sspower
Type: Package
Title: Sample Size and Power Calculation for Regression Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Michael J. Martens <mmartens@mcw.edu>
Maintainer: Michael J. Martens <mmartens@mcw.edu>
Description: Provides functions to compute sample size and power for studies that will be analyzed using generalized linear models and time-to-event regression models (Cox proportional hazards and Fine-Gray models). 
